text: Matěj Beran (born November 11, 1993) is a Czech professional ice hockey player. He is currently playing for HC Dynamo Pardubice of the Czech Extraliga. Beran made his Czech Extraliga debut playing with HC Plzeň during the 2014-15 Czech Extraliga season. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:HC Plzeň players Category:HC Dynamo Pardubice players Category:Czech ice hockey centres
